type="local"
addr="jms-00I7">relation</fr:link> <fr:tex>\mathsf {sq} \colon \mathbb {R}_{ \geq  0} \mathbin { \nrightarrow }   \mathbb {R}</fr:tex> from <fr:ref
addr="jms-00I9"
href="jms-00I9.xml"
taxon="Example"></fr:ref>, and let <fr:tex>\mathsf {neg}  \colon \mathbb {R} \mathbin { \nrightarrow } \mathbb {R}</fr:tex> be the <fr:link
href="jms-00I7.xml"
type="local"
addr="jms-00I7">relation</fr:link> <fr:tex>{ \mathopen {} \left \{ (x,y) \in \mathbb {R}^2 \mid  x = -y \right \} \mathclose {}}</fr:tex>. Then the <fr:link
href="jms-00IN.xml"
type="local"
addr="jms-00IN">relational composite</fr:link> <fr:tex>\mathsf {neg} \circ \mathsf {sq} \colon   \mathbb {R}_{ \geq  0} \mathbin { \nrightarrow } \mathbb {R}</fr:tex> is equal to <fr:tex>\mathsf {sq}</fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 
   
